{"tid":789111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一篇新聞就解釋到香港幾多窮人","createTime":"2018-08-22T04:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T06:23:59.000Z","uid":113626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"082157561b7447b5cc7f8128bfee37f8242a496e","tid":789111,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"政府派錢4000元　最快明年2月1日申請　4月底截止<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波在2月28日發表今屆政府首份《財政預算案》，被部分人批評派糖不均，其後回應民意「補漏拾遺」，<span style=\"color: red;\">宣布向今年內年滿18歲、2017至2018年度無繳交薪俸稅、在港無物業、無領取政府援助、持香港身分證且通常居港的人，發放4000元津貼。而如果薪俸稅退稅及差餉寬免不足4000元的巿民，亦可獲補足差額，目標是在下個財政預算案前發放款項。</span><br />\n<br />\n當局今日向立法會提交文件，當中指出職津處將會推行該計劃，包括開發電腦系統、接收和處理申請、發放款項、處理查詢及投訴、安排宣傳、處理上訴和進行調查，計劃最快於2019年2月1日至 4月30日期間接受申請，為期3個月。<span style=\"color: red;\">當局預計該計劃能讓約300萬人受惠。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時吹到自己月入50k ,退稅連4000$都唔到"},{"pid":"6c8d193eb9f751301d70b9b4832eba4d406f1a93","tid":789111,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:07:19.000Z","msg":"師兄 香港有700幾萬人 有300萬係支那狗 <br />\n有咩咁出奇？？"},{"pid":"7db014cba375036ec7c5aeb98845c35f5e579ede","tid":789111,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-BE5pLriC8OI/WLgfrHyDiNI/AAAAAAAAGfc/atOlgT12hOYdmaT_DrqcfxfwRT-yIkpcwCLcB/s1600/bf2b0aaf616d19f36ced85e8bc7214db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-BE5pLriC8OI%2FWLgfrHyDiNI%2FAAAAAAAAGfc%2FatOlgT12hOYdmaT_DrqcfxfwRT-yIkpcwCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fbf2b0aaf616d19f36ced85e8bc7214db.jpg&h=831ab758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7666b075914d62ba62f800bbacd0ed91f3273c3","tid":789111,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88fd47859771b38863aac10dd23ffb313467fca6","tid":789111,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6c8d193eb9f751301d70b9b4832eba4d406f1a93","t